# Portfolio — deep map

Full-stack **portfolio + banking** app. Angular 17 FE + Express BE. DB via `DB_TYPE`: `mysql` (default) | `mongodb`. Hash routing (`useHash: true`). Auth = localStorage flag + API domain (no JWT).

## Top-level

```
backend/          Express API (server.js → routes → db/utils)
frontend/src/app/ Angular UI (components/services/utils/guards/constants)
scripts/          Python one-off migrations (excel/sql/mongo)
data/             Backups/samples — IGNORE unless asked
docker-compose.yml  mysql + mongo + app
Dockerfile        Multi-stage: ng build → serve from backend/public
.env.example      Root env template
```

