| `db/banking-advanced.js` | Rules, budgets, recurring, transfers, forecast, continuity |
| `routes/*.js` | Thin HTTP; business in db/utils |
| `utils/snapshot-queries.js` | MySQL as-of amount / series / filters for analytics |
| `utils/mongo-analytics.js` | Mongo twin of analytics aggregations |
